{"tid":2223554,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"呢個時勢，好多人有份工仲亞之亞左","createTime":"2020-09-30T02:36:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T12:44:27.000Z","uid":324681,"like":9,"dislike":85,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"4513a4d5381807b8ea78236514f54022900beb70","tid":2223554,"uid":324681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T02:36:14.000Z","msg":"我唔係奴性重<br />\n而係眼見公司生意真係冇以前咁好<br />\n我哋本身返足6日，放勞工假正日，人工勁低但自己度高到冇朋友。朝9晚6唔使ot準時收工。<br />\n家陣老細想大家幫手真正輪休唔好嚮星期日同假日休息，老細本身年終無休日日開門做生意，近年佢開始頂唔順唔想返但又想做生意。<br />\n同事媽聲四起~<br />\n當然我都唔想咁，我都唔鍾意輪休。<br />\n但行內已經開始要員工放無薪假部份更加裁員甚至執笠。<br />\n其實我都想跳槽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fec5738987dc5a5317319554dcdc5b05571d6443","tid":2223554,"uid":100016,"like":111,"dislike":2,"score":109,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T02:37:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2331cf08359f18e355fc9ef1dbabd39e2ea43eb7","tid":2223554,"uid":284432,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T02:46:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"760b5217b5ca1fa6defa2d4e1c2827a020c4adf9","tid":2223554,"uid":324681,"like":1,"dislike":25,"score":-24,"quote":{"pid":"fec5738987dc5a5317319554dcdc5b05571d6443","tid":2223554,"uid":100016,"like":111,"dislike":2,"score":109,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T02:37:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T02:47:34.000Z","msg":"同出面比我好似奴咗D, 工作鍾意一做做到尾先收手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過一夠鐘我就走人~"},{"pid":"41cef64255a00e655ea4a114c1842612d6f54b68","tid":2223554,"uid":81312,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T02:51:05.000Z","msg":"腦細想做生意關我乜事？點解星期日都要返？"},{"pid":"476c1a97398c2b58a69878db800c03e80aec39d2","tid":2223554,"uid":81312,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T02:51:53.000Z","msg":"佢年終無休應份㗎喎"},{"pid":"a291972b93f13ec2a2c06a4cb284bcfe33b4fae5","tid":2223554,"uid":13368,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T02:52:35.000Z","msg":"On9<br />\n新聞嚇鳩你都信<br />\n我嗰行大把人過檔<br />\n我都加咗20%人工"},{"pid":"da75ac1dcc9d9c7a6abf96b875d2b9b057cebed2","tid":2223554,"uid":29226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T02:52:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"204f7ede272cb46ed8eda59b9e21570c7485ac11","tid":2223554,"uid":34867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T02:54:08.000Z","msg":"屌下都唔得呀，家陣同佢有親呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3fbd25d107a633d1b4366bb0388d292fdacbeac","tid":2223554,"uid":324681,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"a291972b93f13ec2a2c06a4cb284bcfe33b4fae5","tid":2223554,"uid":13368,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T02:52:35.000Z","msg":"On9<br />\n新聞嚇鳩你都信<br />\n我嗰行大把人過檔<br />\n我都加咗20%人工"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T02:54:21.000Z","msg":"但我有行家搵地產揸巴士都唔請。。。"},{"pid":"5a55583f5f7aa07e34d70c119eb8ebd226e83452","tid":2223554,"uid":72085,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T02:56:34.000Z","msg":"言下之意即係係健全勞工福利下，你公司會失去競爭力? 而呢個係員工唔接受輪休既錯?"},{"pid":"5e888c569301807d2d5fb1d72e360fbd4fea161c","tid":2223554,"uid":324681,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"5a55583f5f7aa07e34d70c119eb8ebd226e83452","tid":2223554,"uid":72085,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T02:56:34.000Z","msg":"言下之意即係係健全勞工福利下，你公司會失去競爭力? 而呢個係員工唔接受輪休既錯?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T03:12:13.000Z","msg":"我諗其實公司已經算係單方面改變合約。佢係唔啱。<br />\n不過而家佢咁都唔炒人又唔放無薪假（大家都十幾日假未放）同隔離商戶比佢都算係咁。<br />\n我有點冷眼旁觀，因為我冇諗過做落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過同事內地嚟唔識英文唔識電腦又唔識上連登手軟腳軟50幾歲人冇競爭力就真係請佢地要硬食一係把心一橫搵路數。<br />\n我有少少buy&quot;唔鍾意就咪鬼做&quot;。班人嘈足十幾年都仲嚮度做。"},{"pid":"483ff12a60bb85493c7c77930b179155e916cc54","tid":2223554,"uid":378793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T03:14:25.000Z","msg":"紅日返工咁又點"},{"